“Drop worrying about trifles. The future will settle all that. Really, really, really” (my voice suddenly changed to a shrill scream), “what an idiot you are!”

She melted into tears and was all at once a yielding creature quivering on my breast: “Please,” she faltered, “please, forgive me. Oh, I’m a fool, you are right, do forgive me! This awful 